<br>
For Mid:<br>
<br>
Skalds have damage add, speed, and resist chants.  Runies have speed and bubble chants.<br>
<br>
So looks like Mids will potentially have damage add, speed, bubble, and single line resists.  Oh yeah...song of rest!<br>
<br>
For Hib:<br>
Bards have a speed chant, end, power regen, and health regen.  Not sure if hibbie casters have a chant besides speed.<br>
<br>
So Hibs will potentially have speed chant, end regen, power regen, and health regen.  <br>
<br>
For Alb:<br>
<br>
Minstrels have a speed, ablative chant, health regen, and power regen.  I think Alb casters have a bubble chant, and not sure if Albs sorc mez reducer is a chant or a buff.<br>
<br>
So albs will potentially have speed, ablative, health regen, power regen, and bubble.<br>
<br>
