<br>
=========<br>
earth theurgs have bubble same as runies<br>
sorcs have chant mezz reduction <br>
<br>
minst can sorta twist ablative/speed.<br>
<br>
More importantly tho, if there are say...4 minst using this ability with ablative up.<br>
<br>
say you want to hit a target in their sphere of influence, say you are a zerker (pre nerf even).<br>
<br>
with just 4 ablatives running, you will be lucky to do about 130 damage every 3-4 rounds of combat. (using LA)<br>
<br>
if they pop BOF in your targets group (its not area effective), you will be lucky to hit for say,..30 damage in 3 rounds of combat...total.<br>
<br>
bottom line, alb groups will be nearly invincible with this ring in widespread use.<br>
